  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Walliserhof Grand Hotel &amp; Spa is offered on a half board basis with meals being taken in the Cesar Ritz Restaurant.</p>
<p>Breakfast consists of an excellent hot and cold buffet.</p>
<p>Dinner includes a four course evening meal with choice of each course. When the Cesar Ritz Restaurant is not open, you'll have the opportunity to dine around in the two other restaurants,<span> Del Ponte Pizzeria and Fondue-Stübli.</span></p>
<p>Free daily afternoon cake is available between 2-5pm - tea/coffee payable locally.</p>
<p>A Christmas and New Year gala dinner is included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
